Reasoning: The paper presents a heuristic search procedure based on Threshold Accepting to solve timetabling problems, which is a common approach in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and optimization (cs.DS) research. The use of a stochastic neighborhood and the focus on overcoming local optima suggests a machine learning (cs.LG) or neural networks (cs.NE) approach. The implementation of the algorithm also involves the use of data structures and algorithms commonly used in robotics (cs.RO).
